data.description: Redlands -  2 1/2 Acres - POOL underground ,prime residential land with 10 horse barn, riding ring, wash area, paddock, Recreation building, storage building, property fenced 100%, Roof only 5 years old, New AC, Newer gas cooking stove with propane tank, stainless refrigerator, 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, family room, great room with living and dining area, inside laundr room, Kitchen wood cabinets, home in good condition House approx 2200 sf, plus 10 stall barn, and separate recreation building for storage and parties - Priced to SELL !!  Best Value in Redlands on 2  1/2 acres , pool and barn for horses .
